products.name: Black Sneaker
products.des: A 70s style reborn. These men's shoes take inspiration from iconic sport styles of the past and move them into the future. They're crafted with a suede upper and leather-like details. Signature 3-Stripes flash along the sides. Plush midsole cushioning gives comfort to every step
